  <strong>
    Stretch is a leadership and management conference to learn from the bests and stretch yourself. Join us in Budapest, Hungary this December and get inspired by stories from leads and founders of great organisations as they talk about the challenges of leadership and management. First you grew. Now you lead.
  </strong>
</p>

<p>What makes someone a great manager? Why is it important to maintain a great relationship with your peers? What makes you a team lead? Can you learn leadership at all or you have to be born for it? Building and leading successful companies is not a matter of luck. Organization culture, team productivity, setting expectations, handling conflicts, motivation, coaching, leaving your comfort zone—these are everyday phrases of a great lead. You have to stretch yourself to grow yourself and so your team.</p>

